	<ul>
		<li> What is a good algorithm for the emptiness problem?</li>
		<li> Rabin's <i>seminal</i> paper asks for dynamic complexity of probabilistic languages!</li>
		<!--<li> Is the emptiness problem decidable assuming isolated threshold?</li>-->
		<li> What good is the prostochastic theory? Does it have a logical counterpart? What are relevant subclasses of probabilistic automata?</li>
